All Classes

  • All Classes Class Summary Exception Summary 
    Class Description
    Dinner
    Dinner is an object that contains the name of the event, number of people attending, number of non-vegetarian dishes needed, and number of vegetarian dishes needed.
    EventAlreadyPlannedException
    EventAlreadyPlanned is an exception created to avoid someone booking more than one lunch or dinner event for the same date.
    Events
    This is my super events object that the lunch and dinner objects extend from.
    IncorrectRecipientException
    IncorrectRecipient is an exception created to make sure the correct person is taking the mail out of the locker.
    InvalidAmountOfPeopleException
    InvalidAmountOfPeople is an exception created to make sure the number of people for the event stay within the constraints set by the type of event.
    InvalidSizeException
    InvalidSize is an exception created to make sure the size of the mail and the locker is greater than 0.
    Locker
    Locker is an object that contains the dimensions of what it can fit and any mail that may be in it.
    LockerException
    LockerException is created to make sure the locker is empty or will fit the piece of mail trying to be added.
    Lunch
    Lunch is an object that contains the name of the event, number of people attending, and number of sandwiches needed.
    Mail
    Mail is an object that contains the dimensions of what it can fit inside as well as the recipient it is for.
    Recipient
    Recipient is my super object of a person that contains their first name, last name, and email address.
    Schedule
    Schedule is an object that contains the date, any lunch events that are booked, and any dinner events that are booked.
